{"results":[{"aya":"008","id":5720,"locale":"ja","sura":"079","text":"（不信者の）心は，その日戦き震え，","translator":"Unknown"},{"aya":"009","id":5721,"locale":"ja","sura":"079","text":"目を伏せるであろう。","translator":"Unknown"},{"aya":"010","id":5722,"locale":"ja","sura":"079","text":"かれらは言う。「わたしたちは初め（生前）の状態に，本当に返るのでしょうか。","translator":"Unknown"},{"aya":"011","id":5723,"locale":"ja","sura":"079","text":"何と，わたしたちは朽ち果てた骨になってしまったのに。」","translator":"Unknown"},{"aya":"012","id":5724,"locale":"ja","sura":"079","text":"かれらは言う。「その場合（復活），損な戻りです。」","translator":"Unknown"},{"aya":"013","id":5725,"locale":"ja","sura":"079","text":"（復活は），只一声の叫びである。","translator":"Unknown"},{"aya":"014","id":5726,"locale":"ja","sura":"079","text":"見よ，かれらは目覚めて（地上に）現われる。","translator":"Unknown"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":7,"previousPage":"/ja/s079.json","nextPage":"/ja/s079-3.json"}}